name: Bryan Apostol
text: This is a practical joke right? Kasama ba to sa need na ihayag (o mag imbento) ng kung anoanong association to every half-pinoy athlete or actress, and now politicians, that has a claim to fame, just to get noticed by the global community? Seriously.. wtf? 😒
